{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act28side", "eventName": "不義之財", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "CV-ST-3", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "法外之徒", "storyInfo": "潔西卡不願接受家族的蔭庇，選擇與伍德洛一起去往拓荒地。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "42_i10", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰爭結束了，伍迪，你自由了。你可以回到拉特蘭，回到那棟父母留給你的小房子，在門廊前種滿玫瑰與月季……", "name": "魯伯特"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，找一家附近的教堂，把它們繪在天頂上，傾聽每一位來者的禱告，然後讓這些聲音伴你入夢，這樣，你便能安眠一整晚。", "name": "魯伯特"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在倉庫裡找到了你的銃，他的……實在是找不到了，伍迪，就帶上它回去吧。", "name": "魯伯特"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你呢？你要去哪裡？", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要留在這裡……", "name": "魯伯特"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要留在哥倫比亞嗎……可戰爭已經結束了。", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伍迪，你的戰爭結束了，我的才剛剛開始。", "name": "魯伯特"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g9_modernoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伍迪，嘿，伍迪……", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#5$2", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘶……", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還好嗎？", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#5$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我昏迷了多長時間……", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三天。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些孩子看到我受傷了都很緊張，一時下手沒輕重。你被推倒時腦袋撞在了階梯上，當場就昏過去了。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潔西卡她們……", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，她毫髮無傷。至於海倫娜女士，我派了人護送。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "預計半個月後，她就能安然抵達那家賭場，將所有錢洗得乾乾淨淨，再交給那位早已等在拓荒地的西爾維婭。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你沒叫人去追嗎？", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#10$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伍迪，我一早就說了，我只關心合約上的事，上面要求我拖拽地塊到指定的位置，並在拖拽期間維護地塊治安。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#7$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "地塊外的事情，裡面沒提到，我不關心。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伍迪，我是個冷血的混蛋，但我也不喜歡趴在別人的血肉上飽餐。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你打算怎麼處置我？", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在哥倫比亞南部有一幢私宅，裡面有一間很大的花房，是個好地方。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以更名換姓去那裡安度晚年，我會安排好一切。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在那裡住過？", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從沒有，聽地產商是這麼跟我說的。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……謝謝你的好意，但地產商的話信不得。", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然你無意把我交給法庭，那我就要離開了。", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#10$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去找你的朋友？", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#7$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去找我的家人。", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的銃我放在了桌子上，半個月後有最後一列去往拓荒地的車隊……", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_telephonering", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以……", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_telephonering", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可……", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以先接電話。", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#7$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g10_blacksteelarmory", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_222", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要喝茶嗎，先生？一路趕來，真的辛苦了……", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_222", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……呃，謝謝，潔西卡小姐。既然您的家族花費高薪將我僱傭，我理當竭誠為您服務。", "name": "風塵僕僕的律師"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "搶劫銀行是重罪……這官司很難吧。", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_222", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "分情況，不同的需求，不同的難度。", "name": "風塵僕僕的律師"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果您對監獄沒有那麼抗拒的話，我們會為您爭取最短的刑期，舒適的環境，出來後沒人會記得您所做的事情。", "name": "風塵僕僕的律師"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種事我們經常做，只要錢到位就沒什麼難度。", "name": "風塵僕僕的律師"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，還有呢？", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_222", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，很少有人想待在牢獄裡面，我們還有另一套計劃，您可以在家裡面，或者某個風景秀美的別墅裡待上一陣子。", "name": "風塵僕僕的律師"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，也在當局的監視下。", "name": "風塵僕僕的律師"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對你們有難度嗎？", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_222", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有，但不大。", "name": "風塵僕僕的律師"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#14$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_222", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果您一天牢也不想坐，只想假裝無事發生，立刻恢復正常的生活……很難，但也不是不可能。", "name": "風塵僕僕的律師"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……在哥倫比亞，去監獄的罪犯其實很少，更多人是會被發往拓荒地的，對嗎？", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_222", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您放心，潔西卡小姐……有我們在，結果不會糟糕到那個地步。", "name": "風塵僕僕的律師"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……我是說自己想去拓荒地，先生。", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_222", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "風塵僕僕的律師"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我應該在那裡。我觸犯了法律，這是我應該付出的代價。", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_222", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您要我這樣向布林雷先生回覆嗎，潔西卡小姐？對我來說，這才是最有難度的事情。", "name": "風塵僕僕的律師"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……阻止我做想做的事情，才是最難的。", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#13$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為那是完完全全的……不可能。", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_222", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是堅定……", "name": "風塵僕僕的律師"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#15$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是呀，很堅定……比以前的選擇都要堅定。", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#7$2", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$2", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g9_modernoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_telephonering", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真不打算接？", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#6$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伍迪，我從來沒和任何人講過，我真的很討厭電話。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但其實能看出來，現在你的眉頭能夾起一張紙。", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#10$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼明顯嗎？", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#6$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，沒錯，每當電話響起，我只想舉起銃將它射成篩子。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想過無數次，但每一次，我都只能壓抑下衝動，然後將它接起。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是一通電話而已……", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#5$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跟它在戰場上待兩個月，什麼都變了。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#7$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從傍晚守到黎明，你一接起它，裡面的聲音說“進攻”。我只能聽令，帶著手下的士兵去衝鋒陷陣。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從黎明戰鬥至傍晚，你帶著剩下的人回來，還來不及休息，電話又響了。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "裡面的聲音下令“守住陣地”，然後所有人返回前線，繼續無窮無盡的鬥爭。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#7$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#10$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就此分別吧，伍迪，如果我早已失去在你葬禮上致詞的資格，那麼我希望你能答應我唯一的請求。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別死在我不知道的地方。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#2$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……行，有句話留給你。", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#10$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼？", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果回不了頭，回個電話總是可以的，你也不必每次都被動地守著它。", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g9_modernoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#7$2"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望你永遠記得這通電話。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_telephone", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拿起桌上的電話，他按下幾個數字。"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$formal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$2"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您好，行長先生。我剛剛有些事情，沒有接到。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$2"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，拖拽期間出了些亂子。我明白您焦急的心情，但是對我來說，只要將地塊帶到指定位置，任務就算圓滿結束。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$2"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其他一切都算是小插曲，沒人會在意的。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$2"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我明白，那筆錢對您很重要。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$2"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您正在事業上升期，那些從特里蒙來的傢伙會幫您更上一層樓。但是現在錢沒了，我猜他們一定不會放過您。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$2"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，我知道您並不在乎他們。您上面有些更難對付的人，那些人才是真正決定您命運的人。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$2"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，我理解，我都理解……", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$2"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#9$2"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，如果我能幫您補上那個漏洞呢？雖然不是小數目，但我掏得起。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#9$2"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作為回報，您或許也可以幫我個小忙。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#9$2"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$2"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有些文件，希望您能簽署，並在之後保密。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$2"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您那邊有人在敲門？對，看來我的傭兵們把文件送到了。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$2"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈……您不敢簽？", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$2"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這可是次雙贏的合作……", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$2"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "半小時後我會再打一通電話給您，希望到時您已經考慮好了，回頭見。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$2"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_telephone", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請進。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_glassdooropen", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克里夫先生，錢款已經準備好了，只等那位行長先生做決定了。", "name": "秘書"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是……我們前些日子拿下玻利瓦爾的平台時，可比這次順利多了。", "name": "秘書"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那畢竟是玻利瓦爾。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "玻利瓦爾沒有那位掀起風潮的科學家，也沒有擠破頭想抓住每個廢棄地塊的科技企業。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不僅如此，玻利瓦爾在地塊的價格和出讓手續上也很爽快。", "name": "秘書"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟他們並不排斥和我們搞好關係。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "秘書"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，別抱怨事情不順了。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和平的弦繃得越緊，兩頭的人就越想掌握能切斷它的那把快刀。可一旦徹底砍斷，那把刀要麼快點抽身，要麼就只能繼續被握在手裡。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們已經被一個比玻利瓦爾強大得多的傢伙耽誤得太緊太久了。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想讓那個大傢伙稍微鬆一鬆手，甚至硌疼他，讓他知道斷了的弦意味著什麼，我們以後還不知道要處理多少達維鎮這樣的事。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#7$2"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個他不屑放在眼皮下的老舊平台……嘖，說不定它的作用比我們預計的更大。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#7$2"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我們只考慮最切近的影響，黑鋼在玻利瓦爾和哥倫比亞東部邊境設立的這兩處訓練中心，也確實能極大提升這些區域的治安。", "name": "秘書"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，如果連這些都不在乎，我們和那些只知道拿錢辦事的傢伙……不，和那些“大傢伙”，又有什麼區別？", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過那都是以後的事了。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$2"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_telephonering", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$2"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那位行長打回來了，看來這個決定對他來說沒那麼難。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$2"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要一起聽嗎？", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$2"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g10_blacksteelarmory", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$tech_intro", "key": "$tech_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4105_almond_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4105_almond_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我們為什麼要選在這個時候啟航啊……我還想去送送潔西卡和伍德洛先生。", "name": "羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4105_almond_1#8$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別抱怨啦，快來收拾你的衣服吧。", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#3$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "堆得滿地都是……嘖嘖。", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#9$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4105_almond_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼你們都不著急，潔西卡去了拓荒地，以後我們再見面就不知道是什麼時候啦……", "name": "羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4105_almond_1#5$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克里夫先生沒有批准潔西卡的離職申請……就算去了拓荒地，她還是黑鋼的員工。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4105_almond_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼，可是她這次去拓荒地……是、是要服刑的啊……", "name": "羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4105_almond_1#9$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，沒錯……帶著黑鋼員工的身份……和工作。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4105_almond_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……工作？", "name": "羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4105_almond_1#7$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，去哪裡也躲不掉的工作。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#9$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說不定哪天在拓荒地出任務，我們就得去找她。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#9$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4105_almond_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……", "name": "羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4105_almond_1#8$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快把這一地的衣服收起來吧。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#9$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4105_almond_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼嘛……都瞞著我，我還以為以後……", "name": "羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4105_almond_1#5$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不怪我們哦，誰叫你們工程崗總是忙得不見人影。", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#7$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4105_almond_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？這是……什麼？", "name": "羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4105_almond_1#10$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4105_almond_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒什麼，我在衣服口袋裡摸到了一張字條。", "name": "羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4105_almond_1#2$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大驚小怪。又不是鈔票。", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#3$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4105_almond_1#11$1", "duration": 1.0, "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在半個月前，羅拉曾穿著那件外套，擁別了自己的朋友。"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時她遞給了對方一張字條，沒有注意到對方其實也在她口袋裡塞了一張字條。"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "背過房間裡其餘兩人，羅拉展開了那張字條。"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上面有幾個數字，還有一段潦草的話："}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“如果缺經費，就打這個電話。”"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snowconutryinside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_inside", "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$clink"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再來一輪。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士，您已經在這個小酒館坐一晚上了。老闆都快打烊了。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，我認識這裡的老闆。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在等人嗎？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不等，這輩子不等人。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#4$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都是別人等您嗎？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#6$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯……", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能等到您嗎？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等我的人可太多了，你說的哪一位？", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠的不說，說近的，正等您的那位。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能，一定能，我向別人打過包票，肯定是要去見的。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您這樣重信重諾的人不多了，唉，我請您喝一杯吧。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你跟我這麼久，就是為了請我喝一杯嗎？", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不管您信還是不信，我也向人打過包票，一定得讓等您的那個女孩等到您。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您可以叫我蒂拉。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodcracle", "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g12_snowfield", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在一片焦土中，我看見有火星亮起，隨風飄向遠方，又湮滅為煙灰。"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抑或將夜幕灼燒，露出天光。"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$saferoom_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真的打算和我一起去拓荒地嗎？", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道你拋下的是什麼嗎？", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知道。", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愚蠢的決定。", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#15$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，也許幾年後，幾個月後，甚至幾天之後……我就會覺得，自己做了個愚蠢的決定。", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我只能依靠現在，只能依靠此時此刻的心去做出選擇。", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我現在覺得它值得孤注一擲，我就沒有理由不付諸行動。", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那裡真的會有你追逐的東西嗎，潔西卡？", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#14$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前……我總是竭盡全力去追逐一些我根本追不上的東西。", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "童年時我試圖追趕兄姊那比我還高的長腿，少年時祖父去世，我人在異地，又要追趕一場趕不上的葬禮。", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長大後……我又在追趕一場場無法阻止的禍事與紛爭。", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#2$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我永遠在追趕，但永遠也來不及。", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#15$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次不一樣，這次我不追了。", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為從一開始，我就會在。", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那便走吧，潔西卡，做好準備，在那裡一切都要重新來過。", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "42_i13", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼不開心，潔西卡？", "name": "祖父"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的城堡倒了，花了一個下午，現在什麼都沒有了。", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潔西卡，你把城堡堆在沙灘上，它自然會被浪推倒……", "name": "祖父"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是我太笨，沒能給它找個安全的地方。", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我看看你的小腦袋又在胡思亂想什麼了？你是我的孫女，怎麼可能會笨？", "name": "祖父"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是哥哥姐姐都比我聰明……比我懂的多……", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們都是成年人了，自然閱歷要比你豐富，等你長大了，也會像他們一樣。", "name": "祖父"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但那時他們不會更厲害嗎？", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呦……你的怪問題怎麼這麼多……", "name": "祖父"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起……", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別沮喪了……讓我和你一起把沙堡復原吧？", "name": "祖父"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可以嗎……？可是就算復原了，明天還是會被波浪推倒。", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後……什麼都沒有……", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潔西卡，如果你害怕被浪花推倒，那我們就選一片離海水更遠的沙灘，重建一座沙堡。", "name": "祖父"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當一切都失去時，未來仍然存在……我們依然要對它抱有信心。", "name": "祖父"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要懼怕重新來過……", "name": "祖父"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "42_i14", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗯，那便重新來過吧。", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一頂溫暖的帽子被扣在女孩頭上。帽檐很寬，幾乎蓋住她大半張臉。"}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你想哭就哭出來吧……經歷了這麼多……想必也不好受。", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有……", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要為哭泣而感到羞恥……潔西卡，新生都是從哭泣開始的。", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是呼吸的第一步。", "name": "伍德洛"}}, {"id": 455, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 457, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 458, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "42_i15", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1, "x": 0.0, "y": 30.0}}, {"id": 459, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "yTo": 0.0, "duration": 20.0}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 461, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沉默許久後，終於，一聲啜泣從帽子下響起。"}}, {"id": 463, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老人沒有低頭看，而是將目光投向雪原的盡頭。"}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "地平線處的天空被朝霞染紅，倒映在光潔的雪地。"}}, {"id": 465, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那一片朱紅色讓他雙目刺痛，幾欲落下淚水。"}}, {"id": 466, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 467, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 468, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 469, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 470, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 471, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 472, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 473, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 474, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}